asset.author: Dirt Devil
asset.hookText: Vac, dust & reach — versatility to clean where your upright vac can’t. 360° Reach™ Pro speeds through messes from floor to ceiling with Vac+Dust Tools with SWIPES™. Snap on the Crevice Tool and extend your cleaning reach to get the small stuff—high and low. Then clean every part of each step with the Powered Stair & Upholstery Tool. When you’re through, dump the dirt with the touch of a button.

transcripts: Just to reach the dirt. 360 reach gives you the versatility to clean up right back can go from floor to ceiling in seconds with 12 feet of extended reach easily pick up debris with powerful suction. While the washable pads captures the dust and dirt then step up your stair cleaning easily adjusts to cover every part of each step. Even stair risers its power and versatility in the palm of your hand. The dirt devil 363.
